Demo for GraphRAG January-February 2020 

NOTE: GRAPHRAG CAN INCUR HIGH COST FOR API CALLS! 

1. Download graphrag_chinese or graphrag-english from https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1O3VgOmraE3NgNhtHtKeSbXbzikxNX2aI?usp=sharing 

2. Add your OpenAI API key into the .env file. 

3. Query with 
   graphrag.query \                                      
--root ./graphrag-english \
--method global \
"What are the main themes in the data?"

(Change parameters as needed) 

4. If you would like to try other configurations or perform indexing for your own subset of data, follow the official guide: https://microsoft.github.io/graphrag/ 
